<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>For Ifrah | 18th Birthday</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce4ec 0%, #ffebee 100%);
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(255, 77, 109, 0.2);
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 80%;
        }

        h1 { color: #ff4d6d; font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .age { font-size: 6rem; color: #ff758f; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; margin: 10px 0; }
        p { color: #444; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #ff4d6d;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .heart {
            position: absolute;
            color: #ff8fa3;
            font-size: 20px;
            user-select: none;
            animation: float Up 5s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes floatUp {
            0% { transform: translateY(100vh) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
            20% { opacity: 0.8; }
            100% { transform: translateY(-10vh) scale(1.5); opacity: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="glass-card">
        <h1>Happy Birthday, Ifrah! ❤️</h1>
        <p>A beautiful milestone for a beautiful soul.</p>
        <div class="age">18</div>
        <p>I am so proud of the person you've become.<br>Here's to a lifetime of happiness together.</p>
        <div class="signature">With all my love,<br>Saad</div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function createHeart() {
            const heart = document.createElement('div');
            heart.classList.add('heart');
            heart.innerHTML = '❤️';
            heart.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
            heart.style.fontSize = (Math.random() * 20 + 10) + 'px';
            heart.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 2) + 's';
            document.body.appendChild(heart);

            setTimeout(() => { heart.remove(); }, 5000);
        }
        setInterval(createHeart, 250);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
